Achievements.Name: Homerun!
Achievements.Description: Hit a homerun.

Achievements.Name: Grand Salami!
Achievements.Description: Hit a homerun with the bases loaded.

Achievements.Name: Shutout!
Achievements.Description: Pitch a complete season game with a single pitcher without giving up any runs.

Achievements.Name: Wall Catch!
Achievements.Description: Crush the batter's hopes by climbing the wall to snag one out of the sky.

Achievements.Name: Demoralized!
Achievements.Description: Catch the batter looking for a 3rd-out strikeout with the bases loaded.

Achievements.Name: Made the Playoffs!
Achievements.Description: Make it to the playoffs in a season of any length.

Achievements.Name: The Cycle!
Achievements.Description: Hit a single, double, triple and a homerun in a single game with a single player on your team.

Achievements.Name: Champions!
Achievements.Description: Win a championship.

Achievements.Name: Batting Title!
Achievements.Description: Lead the league in batting average with a player on your team at the end of regular season play.

Achievements.Name: Homerun Title!
Achievements.Description: Lead the league in homeruns with a player on your team at the end of regular season play.

Achievements.Name: Triple Crown!
Achievements.Description: Lead the league in each of AVG, HRs and RBIs with players on your team at the end of season play.

Achievements.Name: SMB Master!
Achievements.Description: Win a championship while playing at Ego 80 or higher.

Achievements.Name: Massive Dinger!
Achievements.Description: Hit a homerun over 500 feet.

Achievements.Name: Extra Innings Win!
Achievements.Description: Win a season game in extra innings.

Achievements.Name: 500 Homeruns!
Achievements.Description: Hit a total of 500 homeruns.

Achievements.Name: Offensive Beast!
Achievements.Description: Modify a player on your team to have a rating of 90 or higher in each of Power, Contact and Speed.

Achievements.Name: Defensive Beast!
Achievements.Description: Modify a player on your team to have a rating of 90 or higher in each of Arm, Fielding and Speed.

Achievements.Name: Great Swing!
Achievements.Description: Hit the ball with a perfectly timed power swing (99 swing score).

Achievements.Name: Double Play!
Achievements.Description: Get two outs on the same play.

Achievements.Name: 500 Strikeouts!
Achievements.Description: Strike out a total of 500 batters.

Achievements.Name: Big Ego!
Achievements.Description: Win a season game at Ego 80 or higher.

Achievements.Name: Huge Ego!
Achievements.Description: Win a season game at Ego 90 or higher.

Achievements.Name: Extraordinary Ego!
Achievements.Description: Win a season game at Ego 99.

Achievements.Name: Comeback!
Achievements.Description: Overcome a 5 run deficit for a win in a season game.

Achievements.Name: Golden Sombrero!
Achievements.Description: Strike out 4 times in a single game with a single player.
